data.description: PRICE DROP!!! NEW ROOF!!! FURNITURE INCLUDED! 2BEDROOM, 2 FULL BATH, with an OFFICE/ADDITIONAL BEDROOM quaint home located in the vibrant Solivita Community. This exquisite property offers a stunning living experience in one of the most desirable neighborhoods in the area. As you approach this beautiful natural stone elevation home, you'll be captivated by its charming curb appeal, landscaping, and meticulously maintained exterior lot. Enter the foyer, to your left, is the open floor plan of the living and dining room area. The open-concept floor plan creates a seamless flow between the living spaces, perfect for both entertaining and everyday living. The abundance of natural light fills the home, especially from the sliding doors with the screened-in covered lanai and unique floor design which overlooks the pond view. This outdoor area is great for relaxing with a  good book. To the right of the home is an eat-in kitchen with lots of cabinet space. There is a 2nd bedroom and an office which can be used as a 3rd bedroom if needed. The additional bathroom is in the near hallway alongside the laundry room leading out to the garage. The master bedroom is toward the rear of the home with 2 walk-in closets and a full master bath. The home has INTERIOR NEW PAINT throughout. Residents of Solivita enjoy a wealth of amenities, including a clubhouse, fitness center, swimming pools, walking trails, tennis courts, and much more. The community also offers various social clubs and activities, providing endless opportunities for entertainment and recreation. Conveniently located in Kissimmee, you'll have easy access to a range of shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Don't miss the opportunity to make 497 Grand Canal Dr your new home. Solivita Community is a 55+ community offering luxurious living and a vibrant lifestyle. Schedule your private showing today!
